abstract: >-
  ait is a Git-native version control layer for AI coding agents
  (Claude Code, Codex CLI, Aider, Gemini CLI, Cursor). It adds
  worktree isolation, attempt provenance, cross-agent memory, and
  reviewable promotion on top of Git, with all metadata stored
  locally under .ait/ — no SaaS, no telemetry. Open source under
  MIT, dependency-free Python 3.14+, distributed as ait-vcs on
  PyPI and npm.
